      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nthe only thing I'm worried about is that we'd have to initialize SA handler very often. while this might be OK with POSIX given very small number of changes, with Lustre it's not that nice, probably - we do update many objects on every \"simple\" operation: last_rcvd, llogs, LAST_ID, changelogs, etc.",
